    <p class="lead">We provide the main services customers ask us for across Shropshire, with specialist cleaning for carpets, upholstery, stain removal, commercial carpet cleaning and rugs.</p>
    <div class="grid grid-3" style="margin-top:34px"><article class="card reveal"><img src="./assets/img/truckmount-hero.png" alt="Carpet Cleaning"><div class="card-body"><h3>Carpet Cleaning</h3><p>Deep carpet cleaning for homes and businesses across Shropshire, removing embedded soil, stains and odours with professional extraction equipment.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="./pages/carpet-cleaning.html">Learn more</a></div></article><article class="card reveal"><img src="./assets/img/upholstery-cleaning.png" alt="Upholstery Cleaning"><div class="card-body"><h3>Upholstery Cleaning</h3><p>Professional sofa, armchair and fabric furniture cleaning with safe methods for everyday dirt, spills and odours.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="./pages/upholstery-cleaning.html">Learn more</a></div></article><article class="card reveal"><img src="./assets/img/tile-grout-cleaning.png" alt="Tile and grout cleaning in action"><div class="card-body"><h3>Stain Removal</h3><p>Targeted treatment for tea, coffee, wine, pet accidents and stubborn everyday spills.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="./pages/stain-removal.html">Learn more</a></div></article><article class="card reveal"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505693416388-ac5ce068fe85?q=80&w=1400&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Commercial Cleaning"><div class="card-body"><h3>Commercial Carpet Cleaning</h3><p>Flexible cleaning for offices, shared spaces and commercial premises with minimal disruption.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="./pages/commercial-carpet-cleaning.html">Learn more</a></div></article><article class="card reveal"><img src="./assets/img/rug-cleaning.png" alt="Rug Cleaning"><div class="card-body"><h3>Rug Cleaning</h3><p>Careful rug cleaning for Persian, Oriental and modern area rugs using fibre appropriate methods and controlled drying.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="./pages/rug-cleaning.html">Learn more</a></div></article></div>
  </div>
</section>
