    <h2>Recent customer feedback shown on the public site</h2>
    <p class="lead">The homepage and service pages rely heavily on customer reviews to build trust, especially around sofas, carpets and tile cleaning.</p>
    <div class="grid grid-3" style="margin-top:30px"><article class="review reveal"><div class="stars">★★★★★</div><p>Bought two sofas second hand and Vad did an amazing job cleaning them. He was lovely, very professional and very accommodating with times and days. Pricing was reasonable and well worth it.</p><strong>Molly Rath</strong><span style="color:var(--muted)">January 21, 2026</span></article><article class="review reveal"><div class="stars">★★★★★</div><p>Absolutely excellent service. We have been customers of Vad for several years and he has always done a fantastic job and has done his best to get us seen quickly.</p><strong>Anthony Leslie</strong><span style="color:var(--muted)">January 9, 2026</span></article><article class="review reveal"><div class="stars">★★★★★</div><p>Vad explained everything clearly before treating the stains, worked efficiently, used blow heaters while he worked and left the house spotless. The results and service were excellent.</p><strong>Aoife O'Regan</strong><span style="color:var(--muted)">November 30, 2025</span></article></div>
    <div style="margin-top:26px"><a class="btn btn-primary" href="./pages/reviews.html">Read more reviews</a></div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="section alt">
  <div class="container center">
    <span class="kicker" style="background:var(--brand-soft);color:var(--brand2)">Common questions</span>
    <h2>Helpful information before you book</h2>
    <div class="accordion"><div class="faq-item reveal"><button type="button"><span>How long do carpets take to dry?</span><span>+</span></button><div class="faq-content"><p>Drying time depends on fabric, airflow and soil level, but The Carpet Cleaning Company promotes fast drying results and uses professional drying equipment where needed.</p></div></div><div class="faq-item reveal"><button type="button"><span>Do you clean sofas and armchairs?</span><span>+</span></button><div class="faq-content"><p>Yes. Upholstery cleaning is one of the core services, including sofas, couches, dining chairs and other upholstered furniture.</p></div></div><div class="faq-item reveal"><button type="button"><span>Do you clean tile, grout and stone?</span><span>+</span></button><div class="faq-content"><p>Yes. The public site specifically offers tile, grout and stone cleaning, with optional sealing to help protect surfaces afterwards.</p></div></div><div class="faq-item reveal"><button type="button"><span>Which areas do you cover?</span><span>+</span></button><div class="faq-content"><p>The public service areas include Shrewsbury, Ludlow, Hereford, Telford, Bridgnorth, Leominster, Church Stretton, Oswestry and Kidderminster.</p></div></div></div>
  </div>
</section>


