  </div>
</header>
<section class="hero inner-hero" style="background-image:linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(4,16,30,.82) 0%, rgba(4,16,30,.58) 42%, rgba(4,16,30,.25) 100%), url('../assets/img/upholstery-cleaning.png')">
  <div class="container hero-grid"><div class="hero-copy reveal"><span class="kicker">About The Carpet Cleaning Company</span><h1>A local service built around dependable cleaning results.</h1><p>The homepage introduces Vad as the owner, says he is fully trained and qualified, and positions the business as a trusted service based in Ludlow covering Shropshire, Herefordshire and Worcestershire.</p></div>
