  </form>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="section"><div class="container split"><div class="reveal"><h2>What the public site says about the business</h2><ul class="list-checks"><li>Based in Based in Ludlow, serving Shrewsbury, Hereford and surrounding areas.</li><li>Fully trained and qualified to clean carpets and upholstery.</li><li>Uses professional equipment and products.</li><li>Public service area covers Shropshire and nearby counties.</li></ul></div><div class="photo-frame reveal"><img src="../assets/img/truckmount-hero.png" alt="The Carpet Cleaning Company van mounted cleaning setup"></div></div></section>


<footer class="footer">
