<!doctype html>
<html lang="en-GB">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Blog | The Carpet Cleaning Company</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Blog and advice from The Carpet Cleaning Company.">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../assets/style.css">
</head>
<body>

<div class="topbar">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="mini">
      <span class="pill">Professional carpet, upholstery, rug, stain removal and commercial cleaning across Shropshire, Herefordshire and Worcestershire</span>
    </div>
    <div class="mini">
      <a href="tel:07802563213">07802 563213</a>
      <span>Based in Ludlow, serving Shrewsbury, Hereford and surrounding areas</span>
      <span>Mon – Sat 8am – 6pm</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<header class="site-header">
  <div class="container nav">
    <a class="brand" href="../index.html">
      <img class="brand-logo" src="../assets/img/vka-logo.png" alt="The Carpet Cleaning Company logo">
      <div class="brand-text"><strong>The Carpet Cleaning Company</strong><span>Shropshire Carpet & Upholstery Specialists</span></div>
    </a>
    <button class="mobile-toggle" aria-expanded="false">Menu</button>
    <nav class="nav-links">
      <a href="../index.html">Home</a>
      <a href="../pages/carpet-cleaning.html">Carpet Cleaning</a>
      <a href="../pages/upholstery-cleaning.html">Upholstery</a>
      <a href="../pages/stain-removal.html">Stain Removal</a>
      <a href="../pages/commercial-carpet-cleaning.html">Commercial</a>
      <a href="../pages/rug-cleaning.html">Rug Cleaning</a>
      <a href="../pages/reviews.html">Reviews</a>
      <a href="../pages/gallery.html">Gallery</a>
      <a href="../pages/service-areas.html">Service Areas</a>
      <a href="../pages/contact.html">Contact</a>
    </nav>
    <div class="nav-cta">
      <a class="btn btn-call" href="tel:07802563213">Call 07802 563213</a>
      <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="../pages/contact.html">Get a Quote</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
<section class="hero inner-hero" style="background-image:linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(4,16,30,.82) 0%, rgba(4,16,30,.58) 42%, rgba(4,16,30,.25) 100%), url('../assets/img/truckmount-hero.png')">
  <div class="container hero-grid"><div class="hero-copy reveal"><span class="kicker">Blog</span><h1>Advice and cleaning insights.</h1><p>The public The Carpet Cleaning Company blog currently shows at least one archive article titled “What Is The Cost Of Carpet Cleaning in Wicklow”. This page gives the site a polished blog hub to build from.</p></div>
<div class="hero-card form-glow">
  <h2>Get a fast quote</h2>
  <p>Tell us what you need cleaned and we’ll come back to you as quickly as possible during opening hours.</p>
  <form class="form-grid" action="#" method="post">
    <input class="input" type="text" placeholder="Your name">
    <input class="input" type="email" placeholder="Your email">
    <input class="input" type="tel" placeholder="Your phone">
    <textarea class="textarea" placeholder="What would you like us to clean?"></textarea>
    <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Send your enquiry</button>
  </form>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="section alt"><div class="container grid grid-2"><article class="card blog-card reveal"><div class="card-body"><h3>What is the cost of carpet cleaning in Wicklow?</h3><p>The public site already covers this topic. A stronger version could explain pricing factors such as room size, fibre type, stain severity and travel.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="contact.html">Ask for a quote</a></div></article><article class="card blog-card reveal"><div class="card-body"><h3>How often should you clean upholstery?</h3><p>An ideal support article for homeowners wanting cleaner sofas, lower allergen build up and longer fabric life.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="contact.html">Ask for a quote</a></div></article></div></section>


