  <div class="container hero-grid"><div class="hero-copy reveal"><span class="kicker">Reviews</span><h1>What customers are saying.</h1><p>The public The Carpet Cleaning Company website leans heavily on Google reviews, with positive comments about sofas, carpets, tile cleaning, fast responses and professional service.</p></div>
<div class="hero-card form-glow">
