<section class="section alt center"><div class="container"><h2>Selected public review highlights</h2><p class="lead">These reviews are paraphrase safe summaries drawn from the public review section and reflect the kind of feedback shown across the site.</p><div class="grid grid-3" style="margin-top:30px"><article class="review reveal"><div class="stars">★★★★★</div><p>Bought two sofas second hand and Vad did an amazing job cleaning them. He was lovely, very professional and very accommodating with times and days. Pricing was reasonable and well worth it.</p><strong>Molly Rath</strong><span style="color:var(--muted)">January 21, 2026</span></article><article class="review reveal"><div class="stars">★★★★★</div><p>Absolutely excellent service. We have been customers of Vad for several years and he has always done a fantastic job and has done his best to get us seen quickly.</p><strong>Anthony Leslie</strong><span style="color:var(--muted)">January 9, 2026</span></article><article class="review reveal"><div class="stars">★★★★★</div><p>Vad explained everything clearly before treating the stains, worked efficiently, used blow heaters while he worked and left the house spotless. The results and service were excellent.</p><strong>Aoife O'Regan</strong><span style="color:var(--muted)">November 30, 2025</span></article><article class="review reveal"><div class="stars">★★★★★</div><p>Great service. Very professional from start to finish. Very happy with the results. My 18 year old kitchen tiles are looking great.</p><strong>G Walsh</strong><span style="color:var(--muted)">May 15, 2025</span></article><article class="review reveal"><div class="stars">★★★★★</div><p>I had my sofa and rug cleaned by Vad. Efficient, punctual and friendly. Excellent results on both.</p><strong>Siún O'Mahoney</strong><span style="color:var(--muted)">May 10, 2025</span></article><article class="review reveal"><div class="stars">★★★★★</div><p>Fantastic job cleaning my carpets and two sofas. They all looked like new and I would highly recommend Vad for his friendly, professional service.</p><strong>Hannah Tobin</strong><span style="color:var(--muted)">April 21, 2025</span></article></div></div></section>


