<section class="section"><div class="container split"><div class="reveal"><span class="kicker" style="background:var(--brand-soft);color:var(--brand2)">Local service page</span><h2>Carpet Cleaning in Carlow with clear local coverage.</h2><p class="lead">If you are looking for carpet cleaning in Carlow, The Carpet Cleaning Company offers a professional quote first service backed by specialist equipment, dependable communication and visible results.</p><ul class="list-checks"><li>Local service for homes and businesses in Carlow</li><li>Fast drying and professional methods</li><li>Honest advice before work starts</li><li>Quote driven booking process</li></ul></div><div class="photo-frame reveal"><img src="../../assets/img/truckmount-hero.png" alt="Truck mounted carpet cleaning system"></div></div></section>
<section class="section alt center"><div class="container"><span class="kicker" style="background:var(--brand-soft);color:var(--brand2)">How we work</span><h2>Our process for carpet cleaning in Carlow</h2><div class="grid grid-2 process" style="margin-top:30px"><article class="card reveal"><div class="card-body"><h3>Inspection</h3><p>Inspection of fibres, stains and traffic lanes</p></div></article><article class="card reveal"><div class="card-body"><h3>Targeted</h3><p>Targeted pre treatment to loosen soil and marks</p></div></article><article class="card reveal"><div class="card-body"><h3>Deep</h3><p>Deep extraction cleaning with professional equipment</p></div></article><article class="card reveal"><div class="card-body"><h3>Fast</h3><p>Fast drying setup and final check before we leave</p></div></article></div></div></section>
<section class="section center"><div class="container"><span class="kicker" style="background:var(--brand-soft);color:var(--brand2)">Recent feedback</span><h2>What customers say about The Carpet Cleaning Company</h2><div class="grid grid-2" style="margin-top:28px"><article class="review reveal"><div class="stars">★★★★★</div><p>I was really impressed with the service. Very responsive, arrived on time and did an amazing job. Our furniture was very dirty but now looks and smells like new.</p><strong>Bartlomiej Hupa</strong></article><article class="review reveal"><div class="stars">★★★★★</div><p>Bought two sofas second hand and Vad did an amazing job cleaning them. Very professional, accommodating and well worth it for the great result.</p><strong>Molly Rath</strong></article></div></div></section>
<section class="section alt"><div class="container"><div class="promo reveal"><h2>More services available in Carlow</h2><p>Customers often book more than one service at the same time, especially when carpets, upholstery and hard floors all need attention.</p><div class="grid grid-3" style="margin-top:22px"><article class="card reveal"><div class="card-body"><h3>Upholstery Cleaning</h3><p>Safe upholstery cleaning for sofas, armchairs and fabric seating using methods matched to the material and level of soiling.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="./kidderminster-upholstery-cleaning.html">View page</a></div></article><article class="card reveal"><div class="card-body"><h3>Tile, Grout & Stone Cleaning</h3><p>Restore the look of tile, grout and stone surfaces with deep hard floor cleaning and optional sealing for longer lasting results.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="./carlow-stain-removal.html">View page</a></div></article><article class="card reveal"><div class="card-body"><h3>Commercial Cleaning</h3><p>Professional commercial cleaning to help remove dust, allergens, odours and marks for a fresher and healthier sleeping environment.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="./carlow-commercial-cleaning.html">View page</a></div></article></div></div></div></section>
